thread.title: CHRISTY
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by CHRISTY

author: CHRISTY
title: CHRISTY
text:
The pick up and paperwork for this car was efficient. No extra insurance charges or fees like I've experienced with other car rentals in the past and a great rate for petrol if you want to prepay for the tank.
Key drop box for early morning returns was great too. Simple!
